  ],
  "remarks": "LLC SPA “Izhevsk Unmanned Systems” is a Russian company which develops, produces, repairs and maintains unmanned aerial vehicles (UAV), special equipment and scientific and technical products. The company is actively involved in the Russian UAV sector (for example, it develops technologies and tests and also conducts specialist training) and therefore materially supports the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the illegal annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine. LLC SPA “Izhevsk Unmanned Systems” has created military drones of the type “Granat”, “Tachyon” and “Kub”, which are used by the Russian Armed Forces in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Therefore, the company is materially supporting actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}